page.title: 12DAY IN THE LIFE OF K.McLEOD
page.content: {ARISE 0620 {PRIVATE PRAYERS 0630 {STUDY,WRITING FOR DURHAM UNIV.TO 0730 {COMMUNION THORNTON WATLASS 0800 {W0RKING CLERGY BREAKFAST T0 0910 {CALLING BEDALE CHURCH TO 0930 {HOSPITAL VISTING 0920 TO 0930 {FETCHING LOCAL SCHOOL CHILDREN 0948 {VISITING PARISHIONER TO 0950 {VICARAGE, INSPECT LIBRARY BOOKS FROM {1660 {CORRESPONDENCE, PRIVATE COMMUNIONS {TO 1030 {TRIP TO CHURCH 1033 {CHRISTENING CONSULTATION TO 1050 {VISITING PARISHIONERS TO 1140 {CHILDREN BACK TO SCHOOL 1150 {LUNCHTIME TO 1255 MEET CHILDREN {PRIVATE COMMUNION TO 1315 {VISITING PARISHIONERS,DELIVERIES {AND HOSPITAL VISITS TO 1520 {RETURN CHILDREN TO SCHOOL 1530
